PROJETO-DE-PESQUISA.DESCRICAO-DO-PROJETO:
The general objective of this project is to reduce the vulnerability of the civil population to catastrophes, thus diminishing casualties, people?s suffering, and damage to private and public property, through improved response to these events. The specific goal is to generate IT solutions to:
1.	Help firefighters to get to the disaster area in minimum time by giving online advice to the drivers;
2.	Brief firefighters with relevant information from the event during their moving to the disaster area;
3.	Coordinate firefighters? activities when a disaster has occurred;
4.	Provide firemen with awareness of the available physical resources, and manage their sharing;
5.	Support firemen?s decision making at several levels (command post, team leaders and rescuers).

